><![CDATA[SELECT
    source_id,
    ra,
    dec,
    phot_g_mean_mag
FROM gaiadr3.gaia_source
WHERE phot_g_mean_mag < 6
ORDER BY phot_g_mean_mag ASC
]]></INFO>
